query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('actions-on-google',
'boost-spirit',
'cakephp-3.0',
'clr',
'conda',
'dropdown',
'es6-promise',
'fortran90',
'game-engine',
'glut',
'java-web-start',
'native',
'pyodbc',
'sip',
'structuremap');
